File:Cytisus scoparius2.jpg|Grasses, trees and shrubs have a much higher biomass than the animals that [[Heterotroph|consume them]]
File:Bluegreen algae.jpg|The total biomass of bacteria may equal that of plants.&lt;ref name=&quot;Whitman etal&quot; /&gt;
